-------------------------------------
Running the APB slave MiniTB example:
-------------------------------------

Step 1) Source the MiniTB setup script for 1-time setup

  For bash users:
    >cd ../../../ && source Setup.bsh && cd -

  For csh users:
    >cd ../../../ && source Setup.csh && cd -

Step 2) Run with your simulator of choice

  For Cadence Incisive users:
    >run_miniTB.pl -ius ahb_slave_miniTB.f

  For Mentor Questa users:
    >run_miniTB.pl -questa ahb_slave_miniTB.f

  For Synopsys VCS users:
    >run_miniTB.pl -vcs ahb_slave_miniTB.f


-------------------------------------
Don't forget to read the miniTB/README for instructions on
how to setup the miniTB test environment and instructions for
building your own tests.

